        <mxCell id="GhEXK6oo9Vz2HnmgyGiv-193" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;" value="The database schema satisfies the requirements of the First, Second, and Third Normal Forms (1NF, 2NF, 3NF):&#xa;&#xa;&#xa;- 1NF: All attributes contain atomic values, and there are no repeating groups.&#xa;- 2NF: All non-key attributes are fully dependent on the primary key.&#xa;- 3NF: There are no transitive dependencies; data is separated into related tables using foreign keys." vertex="1">
